                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Pathfinder #161: Belly of the Black Whale pg. 84",
                        "alt": "Pathfinder #161: Belly of the Black Whale pg. 84",
                        "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq023dz"
                    },
                    "page": 84
                }
            ],
            "html": "An oddity even among the strange creatures of the <a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Planes\">First World</a> of the fey, the aquatic minchgorm is a monstrous alien maw ringed with writhing tendrils. It interacts with the world through grasping, speaking simulacra that it magically shapes from water.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Fey</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a></u>)</b>: DC 43"
        }
    ],
